_sText: This is the best AWP map out, i had it in as J_ROCK_ but that is the mapper not the map name this map name Snipe_Out__2.  This map is great, it test your skill as a sniper it also has an area in the middle you can spawn to where you fight with knifes and nades. Unlike other AWP maps this one dosent get boreing.  This map gets extremly fun when there is at least 3 or more to a side , I think it can hold about 36 plus people, not sure. But if you are and admin of a clan or have alot of traffic at your server thhis is an awsome AWP map GREAT DOWNLOAD have fun GJ J_ROCK_
